headline: Autodesk & PTC, Workday, Estée Lauder: Trending Tickers
summary: Autodesk (ADSK) is reportedly considering a takeover of rival software provider PTC (PTC), according to Bloomberg. Workday (WDAY) stock is under pressure after Piper Sandler analysts downgraded their rating to Underweight from Neutral and cut their price target to $235, citing artificial intelligence (AI) risk and weak demand. Bank of America analysts reinstated coverage of Estée Lauder (EL) with a Buy rating and $110 price target. headline: Simpplr Completes Workday Design Badge Integration
summary: Simpplr, Inc., the leading AI-powered EX platform for unifying employee engagement, enablement and services, today announced that it has achieved Workday Design Approved Integration status. Simpplr now integrates with Workday's comprehensive HR and financial management capabilities, empowering organizations to streamline workflows, enhance employee engagement, and boost productivity.
